lead_paragraph: England's Football Association has launched an inquiry into the violence that marred Wednesday's League Cup tie between West Ham United and Chelsea at the London Stadium while the hosts said 200 people face banning orders.

headline.print_headline: FA Probes Violence at West Ham, 200 Face Banning Orders
